properties.SOURCE_DETAIL: ILOSTAT, indicator Female share of employment in senior and middle management (%). Available at www.ilo.org/ilostat -> Browse by subject -> Yearly indicators -> Employment. For the specific sources by country, refer to the table in ILOSTAT directly.
